---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const transparencyPoints = [
  'No conversation logging',
  'No account profiling',
  'No analytics trackers',
  'No data sale or transfer',
];
---

<Base
  title="adblocked.ai Privacy and Security"
  description="adblocked.ai keeps your AI conversations on your device with transparent, privacy-first design."
>
  <section class="bg-off-white py-20 dark:bg-charcoal">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-navy dark:text-white">Privacy and Security</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base text-gray-muted">
        A tool that claims to give you control over AI must start by giving you control over the tool itself.
      </p>

      <article class="reveal mt-8 rounded-xl border border-border-light bg-white p-6 dark:border-border-light/20 dark:bg-charcoal/50">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-navy dark:text-white">What We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-gray-muted">
          Nothing. adblocked.ai runs locally in your browser. Conversation data never leaves your device.
          We have no servers receiving your data, no databases storing your conversations, and no way to
          access what you say even if we wanted to.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="reveal mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border-light bg-white p-6 dark:border-border-light/20 dark:bg-charcoal/50">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-navy dark:text-white">Transparency</h2>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-base text-gray-muted">
          {transparencyPoints.map((point) => (
            <li>{point}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-muted">
          Source code visibility and auditability are core parts of the product. Every decision the
          extension makes is inspectable. A tool that claims to surface hidden influence cannot itself
          be a black box.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="reveal mt-6 rounded-xl border border-border-light bg-white p-6 dark:border-border-light/20 dark:bg-charcoal/50">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-navy dark:text-white">Privacy by Design</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-gray-muted">
          adblocked.ai is built around privacy-by-default principles aligned with GDPR expectations
          for data minimization and user control. This is a design choice, not a compliance exercise.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
